===Etymology 2===
Probably from [[vingt-un]], and obsolete variant of [[vingt-et-un]], from French, literally ‘twenty-one’.

====Noun====
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{cattag|Card games}}: A card game in which the object is to obtain cards whose value adds up to, or nearly to, 21 but not exceed it.

=====Synonyms=====
*(''card game''): [[vingt-et-un]]

